{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777016082620,"sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_3tmJHA6mfubnAvkr7gTM71IO","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\.agent-project\\tasks\\task-0001.json\n+{\n+  \"id\": \"task-0001\",\n+  \"title\": \"Build project-manager v0.1\",\n+  \"type\": \"implement\",\n+  \"status\": \"review\",\n+  \"priority\": \"high\",\n+  \"phase\": \"validation\",\n+  \"owner\": \"assistant\",\n+  \"depends_on\": [],\n+  \"blocks\": [],\n+  \"tags\": [\"schema\", \"registry\", \"query\", \"mycli\"],\n+  \"acceptance_criteria\": [\n+    \"Project-manager package exists under agent-system-rules\",\n+    \"mycli project-manager commands are registered\",\n+    \"project-manager skill is discoverable via skill-library\",\n+    \"init/register/query/get/status commands work\",\n+    \"ongoing and finite project examples exist\"\n+  ],\n+  \"created_at\": \"2026-04-24T15:33:51+08:00\",\n+  \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-24T15:35:00+08:00\"\n+}\n+\n*** Add File: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\.agent-project\\next-actions\\next-0001.json\n+{\n+  \"id\": \"next-0001\",\n+  \"title\": \"Decide next command surface\",\n+  \"type\": \"decide\",\n+  \"status\": \"open\",\n+  \"priority\": \"high\",\n+  \"owner\": \"千束\",\n+  \"blocks\": [\"task-0002\"],\n+  \"reason\": \"The core registry/query system is usable; the next design decision is whether to add update-status, task add, and next-action add commands immediately.\",\n+  \"created_at\": \"2026-04-24T15:35:00+08:00\",\n+  \"due_at\": null\n+}\n+\n*** Add File: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\.agent-project\\decisions\\ADR-0001-project-structure.md\n+# ADR-0001: Use per-project project.json plus global registry\n+\n+## Status\n+\n+Accepted\n+\n+## Context\n+\n+Project Manager must support durable project state and cross-project queries by name, type, mode, lifecycle, phase, activity, health, delivery, attention, owner, domain, and tags.\n+\n+The workspace contains heterogeneous projects and capability packages, so a single repository-level build or project model is not sufficient.\n+\n+## Decision\n+\n+Each managed project owns `.agent-project/project.json` as its source of truth.\n+\n+Project Manager maintains a generated global `registry.json` for fast query and dashboard-style listing.\n+\n+## Consequences\n+\n+- Project state stays near the project.\n+- The registry can be rebuilt from project files.\n+- Queries can be fast without scanning the workspace every time.\n+- The model can support both finite and ongoing projects.\n+\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA agent_workspace/capability-library/agent-system-rules/project-manager/.agent-project/tasks/task-0001.json\nA agent_workspace/capability-library/agent-system-rules/project-manager/.agent-project/next-actions/next-0001.json\nA agent_workspace/capability-library/agent-system-rules/project-manager/.agent-project/decisions/ADR-0001-project-structure.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\.agent-project\\tasks\\task-0001.json\n===================================================================\n--- D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\.agent-project\\tasks\\task-0001.json\n+++ D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\.agent-project\\tasks\\task-0001.json\n@@ -0,0 +1,21 @@\n+{\n+  \"id\": \"task-0001\",\n+  \"title\": \"Build project-manager v0.1\",\n+  \"type\": \"implement\",\n+  \"status\": \"review\",\n+  \"priority\": \"high\",\n+  \"phase\": \"validation\",\n+  \"owner\": \"assistant\",\n+  \"depends_on\": [],\n+  \"blocks\": [],\n+  \"tags\": [\"schema\", \"regist