{"type":"text","timestamp":1777016152168,"sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","part":{"id":"prt_dbe6aa03d0015v6RA0cquIKLYy","messageID":"msg_dbe69ff74001ITQ3kny5Mt4Ztr","sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","type":"text","text":"已继续优化，并且已经把 `project-manager` 自己作为一个真实项目注册进去了。\n\n## 做了什么\n\n### 1. 优化默认 registry 路径\n\n之前默认 registry 写在源目录：\n\n```text\nagent-system-rules/project-manager/registry.json\n```\n\n我已经改成优先写入 mycli 包目录：\n\n```text\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\project-manager\\registry.json\n```\n\n如果 mycli 包目录不存在，才回退到源目录。\n\n这样更符合使用直觉：\n\n```text\nmycli project-manager query\n```\n\n默认查询的是 mycli 侧 registry。\n\n---\n\n### 2. 把 project-manager 自己注册为项目\n\n已在这里创建：\n\n```text\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\.agent-project\\\n```\n\n包含：\n\n```text\nproject.json\nstatus.md\ntasks/\nnext-actions/\ndecisions/\ncontext/\noperations/\nartifacts/\nruns/\nhandoffs/\nreviews/\n.generated/\n```\n\n项目 ID：\n\n```text\nproject-manager\n```\n\n当前状态：\n\n```text\ntype: capability\nmode: finite\nlifecycle: active\nphase: validation\nactivity: in_progress\nhealth: green\ndelivery: usable\nattention: needs_validation\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. 补了项目内部管理文件\n\n新增任务：\n\n```text\n.agent-project/tasks/task-0001.json\n```\n\n内容是：\n\n```text\nBuild project-manager v0.1\nstatus: review\n```\n\n新增推进项：\n\n```text\n.agent-project/next-actions/next-0001.json\n```\n\n内容是：\n\n```text\nDecide next command surface\n```\n\n新增决策记录：\n\n```text\n.agent-project/decisions/ADR-0001-project-structure.md\n```\n\n记录了核心决策：\n\n```text\n每个项目用 .agent-project/project.json 作为 source of truth\nproject-manager 维护全局 registry.json 作为查询缓存\n```\n\n---\n\n## 验证通过\n\n### 查询 project-manager\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --id project-manager\n```\n\n输出正常：\n\n```text\nproject-manager | Project Manager | capability | finite | active | validation | in_progress | green | usable\n```\n\n### 查看状态页\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager status project-manager\n```\n\n输出正常，能看到当前状态和 next action。\n\n### 别名查询\n\n我给它加了 aliases：\n\n```text\n项目管理器\nproject manager\npm\n```\n\n验证：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --name pm\n```\n\n能查到 `project-manager`。\n\n### lifecycle + phase 查询\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --lifecycle active --phase validation\n```\n\n能查到 `project-manager`。\n\n### Python 编译检查\n\n```powershell\npython -m py_compile D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\src\\project_manager.py\n```\n\n通过。\n\n---\n\n## 当前可用命令\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager init <project-root> --id <id> --name <name> --type <type> --mode finite|ongoing\nmycli project-manager register <project-root>\nmycli project-manager scan [roots...]\nmycli project-manager refresh [roots...]\nmycli project-manager list\nmycli project-manager query [filters]\nmycli project-manager get <id-or-name>\nmycli project-manager status <id-or-name>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 当前 project-manager 项目状态\n\n可以认为现在这个项目已经进入：\n\n```text\nactive / validation / in_progress\n```\n\n下一步最合理的是做：\n\n```text\nupdate-status\ntask add/list/update\nnext-action add/list/update\n```\n\n也就是把“能查询项目”推进到“能持续维护项目”。","time":{"start":1777016152125,"end":1777016152166}}}
